    </div>
    <div class="rights flex-row">
        <h4 class="text-gray">
             made by
            <a href="https://www.fa-linkedin.com/in/tausifmahmud" target="_black">Tausif Mahmud &nbsp; &nbsp;<i class="fab fa-linkedin"></i></a>
